EmailTemplate.description: Email to those who attended Explore Year 7 to advise applications for 2018 closing
EmailTemplate.name: Year 7 2018 applications closing
EmailTemplate.subject: Applications closing for Year 7, 2018
EmailTemplate.textOnly:
Dear {!Lead.FirstName}
Applications for Year 7, 2018 close on Friday 9 June
Thank you again for attending our recent Explore Year 7 event.
We are delighted to receive applications for Year 7, 2018 however applications will be closing on Friday 9 June.
If you wish to apply, please complete the attached Application for Enrolment Form and submit either in person, via post or email to Robyn Pedley rpedley@sacs.nsw.edu.au. Once received, Robyn will be in contact to arrange an enrolment interview with me.
If you have any questions at all, please contact me directly.
Regards
Bruce Perry Registrar/Mathematics Teacher
St Andrew's Cathedral School
Sydney Square, Sydney NSW 2000, Australia direct +61 2 9286 9507 mobile 0418 255 923 email BPerry@sacs.nsw.edu.au phone +61 2 9286 9500 fax +61 29286 9550
